If you’re trying to get someone into these groups, what better way to go than to follow the recruitment model that so many have already followed,” Kohlmann said.
The model is now much more based on the Internet.
Tens of Thousands Demonstrate in Copenhagen for Climate Action
Tens of thousands of protesters marched through the streets here on Saturday, demanding that the negotiators at the city’s Bella Congress Center take more bold action on climate protection.
Demonstrators said 100,000 people had joined the event, while police estimates were about 25,000.
