That’s part of the reasons why I decided to participate in the big demonstration – to deliver the word and appeal to world leaders to reach a fair, ambitious and binding agreement, she said.
It’s not an easy task, but it needs to be done now and there’s no way around it anymore.
Police prevented protesters from getting too close to the Bella Center, saying they had arrested 19 people, mainly because they were either masked or carrying pocket knives.
